    // Caixa de busca: ao subir a tecla
    function acheFacilCampoBuscaSobeTecla() {
        clearInterval(acheFacilTeclaTimeOut);
        // acheFacilTeclaTimeOut = setTimeout("acheFacilBuscaSugestoes()", 125);
        acheFacilTeclaTimeOut = setTimeout("acheFacilBuscaSugestoesA()", 125);
        
    }

    // Caixa de busca: ao ganhar o foco
    function acheFacilCampoBuscaGanhaFoco() {
        if (document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_AcheFacil_5_txtBusca").value == sAcheFacilTextoInicial)
            document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_AcheFacil_5_txtBusca").value = "";
    }

    // Caixa de busca: ao perder o foco
    function acheFacilCampoBuscaPerdeFoco() {
        if (document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_AcheFacil_5_txtBusca").value == "")
            document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_AcheFacil_5_txtBusca").value = sAcheFacilTextoInicial;
        clearInterval(acheFacilTeclaTimeOut);
        clearInterval(acheFacilEscondeSugTimeOut);
        acheFacilEscondeSugTimeOut = setTimeout("acheFacilEscondeSugestoes()", 250);
    }

    // Opcoes de busca: ao alterar opcao
    function acheFacilMudaOpcaoDeBusca() {
        acheFacilCampoBuscaSobeTecla();        
    }

    // Ao carregar a pagina
    $(document).ready(function() {
        document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_AcheFacil_5_txtBusca").value = sAcheFacilTextoInicial;
        acheFacilEscondeSugestoes();
    });

    // Valida os dados para execucao da busca normal (nao sugestao)
    function acheFacilValidaTextoParaBusca() {
        var sTexto = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_AcheFacil_5_txtBusca").value;
        if (sTexto == "") {
            return false;
        } else if (sTexto == sAcheFacilTextoInicial) {
            return false;
        } else {
            if (sTexto.length < 3) {
                window.alert("Digite pelo menos 3 caracteres para realizar a busca!");
                return false;
            } else {
                return true;
            }
        }
    }

    // Botao de busca: Ao clicar
    function acheFacilBotaoBuscaClique() {
        if (acheFacilValidaTextoParaBusca()) {
            document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_AcheFacil_5_btnBuscar").click();
        }
    }

    // Caixa de busca: ao pressionar tecla (onKeyPress)
    function acheFacilCampoBuscaApertaTecla(e) {

        var e = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_ContentPlaceHolderDefault_AcheFacil_5_txtBusca");
        e.autocomplete = 'off'; 
    
        var KEY_ENTER_CODE = 13;
        var keyCode;
        if (e.srcElement) keyCode = e.keyCode;
        if (e.target) keyCode = e.which;
        if (keyCode == KEY_ENTER_CODE) {
            acheFacilBotaoBuscaClique();
            return false;
        } else {
            return true;
        }
    }
    
    // Caixa de busca: ao descer tecla (onKeyDown)
    function acheFacilCampoBuscaDesceTecla(e) {
        var KEY_DOWN_CODE = 40;
        var objLink;
        
        var keyCode;
        if (e.srcElement) keyCode = e.keyCode;
        if (e.target) keyCode = e.which;
        
        if (keyCode == KEY_DOWN_CODE) {
            if (document.getElementById("ache_facil_lista_sugestoes").style.visibility == "visible") {
                objLink = document.getElementById("af_link_sugestao_0");
                if (objLink) objLink.focus();
            }
            return false;
        } else {
            return true;
        }
    }
    
    // Links das sugestoes: onKeyDown
    function acheFacilNavegaSugestoes(codigoDoItem, e) {
        var KEY_UP_CODE = 38;
        var KEY_DOWN_CODE = 40;
        var objLink;
        
        var keyCode;
        if (e.srcElement) keyCode = e.keyCode;
        if (e.target) keyCode = e.which;
        
        if (keyCode == KEY_UP_CODE) {
            if (codigoDoItem == 0) {
